@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam node {
  BackgroundColor #F8F9FA
  BorderColor #333333
}

title Deployment Diagram - MoldProject

node "ESP32 Devices\n(Edge Sensors)" as ESP32
node "Wi-Fi / Gateway" as Gateway

node "Firebase Hosting\n(Frontend)" as Hosting
node "Firebase Authentication" as Auth
database "Firestore (Realtime DB)" as Firestore
cloud "Cloud Functions (Backend)" as Functions
component "Email Service (SMTP/SES)" as Email
node "GCP Analytics Cluster\n(Hadoop/HDFS / Batch)" as Analytics

ESP32 --> Gateway : HTTP / MQTT
Gateway --> Functions : HTTPS (webhook)
Functions --> Firestore : read / write
Hosting --> Auth : signIn / token
Hosting --> Firestore : read / write (client SDK)
Functions --> Email : send notification
Functions --> Analytics : export data / batch job
Firestore --> Analytics : export / export-trigger

note right of ESP32
  - Edge devices (ESP32)
  - Send sensor logs (temp, humidity, wifi)
end note

note left of Hosting
  - Web UI served from Firebase Hosting
  - Uses Firebase SDK to read/write Firestore
end note

note bottom of Analytics
  - Periodic batch ingestion from Firestore
  - Long-term analytics and model training
end note

@enduml
